import { Component, OnInit, ViewChild } from '@angular/core'; import { ReactiveFormsModule, Validators } from '@angular/forms'; import { FormBuilder, FormGroup } from '@angular/forms'; import { PrimeNGConfig } from 'primeng/api'; @Component({ selector: 'app-root', templateUrl: './app.component.html', styleUrls: ['./app.component.css'], }) export class AppComponent implements OnInit { blockedPanel = false; jsonData = ''; apiResponse = ''; cuentaForm: FormGroup; transaccionForm: FormGroup; selectedFormType: string = 'cuenta'; formTypes: any[]; constructor( private primengConfig: PrimeNGConfig, private formBuilder: FormBuilder ) { this.cuentaForm = this.formBuilder.group({ id: ['', Validators.required], tarjetaActiva: [false, Validators.required], limiteDisponible: ['', Validators.required], }); this.transaccionForm = this.formBuilder.group({ id: ['', Validators.required], comerciante: ['', Validators.required], cantidad: ['', Validators.required], tiempo: ['', Validators.required], }); this.formTypes = [ { label: 'Cuenta', value: 'cuenta' }, { label: 'Transacción', value: 'transaccion' }, ]; } onSubmit() { let data; if (this.selectedFormType === 'cuenta') { data = this.cuentaForm.value; } else if (this.selectedFormType === 'transaccion') { data = this.transaccionForm.value; } // Aquí, enviar 'data' a tu servicio API... } ngOnInit() { this.primengConfig.ripple = true; } }
